name: The Unknown Projects
description:
This game combines all the projects  I've started and could not or did not want to finish. Some of these games had really unique ideas and other not so much. I wish I had the knowledge and the skill set to make my dream game. Maybe in time. But have fun exploring my creative mind.

Future

I am currently working on my new biggest project. This game will be out on steam and not on itch.io stay tuned if your interested.
